data.description: JUST UNDER HALF AN ACRE IN TOWN! Listed as a 3 bedroom 2 bath home, the original garage was converted into a 3rd non-conforming bedroom. The kitchen and living room areas feel warm and spacious, with a large separate laundry room off the kitchen. Beyond the laundry room is the door to your fenced-in backyard oasis that contains the shop and a 4'x20' garden spot that waits for your Spring touches! The master bedroom comes equipped with a newly remodeled bath and walk-in shower. The detached 2-car garage (25' x 32') is a solid concrete block shop. It comes wired 220, has heat, and an 11' electric overhead door. The addition added to the back of the shop can be used for equipment, animals, or storage. The 'she-shed' comes with electric and a window unit making it perfect for doing crafts or even housing an extra weekend guest! So many things to love about this large property in the heart of Springfield MO!
